{"tid":984630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長洲東灣泳灘驚現豬屍，非洲豬瘟殺到黎？","createTime":"2019-01-17T03:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T05:03:37.000Z","uid":18105,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4eea840ecfc462dc7a199ffe9f51e78bd4b41f58","tid":984630,"uid":18105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"長洲東灣泳灘發現豬屍，今早(17日)10時27分，有市民在泳灘上發現一頭約3呎長的死豬屍體，由於擔心是大陸病死豬隻漂洋過海「登陸」，於是報警，警方正封鎖現場調查。 <br />\n<br />\n內地非洲豬瘟爆發情況嚴重，內地曾有24個省份發生過家豬和野豬疫情，累計撲殺生豬91.6萬頭；上月19日，台灣宜蘭縣利澤沙灘亦發現一頭死豬屍體，隨即引起台灣網民恐慌。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117104900135-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fbkn-20190117104900135-0117_00822_001.html&d=wupA0mMK9VTR1jnO51Ll3tU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=22c1b64b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117104900135-0117_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"47257bedc8815c784564cfe8844ef8ebcf511606","tid":984630,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:16:49.000Z","msg":"終於到了"},{"pid":"fb3ae5d83467089f798eca9f8a2b3f3f2851d83a","tid":984630,"uid":47359,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:27:19.000Z","msg":"一日唔傳人都冇人關心"},{"pid":"eac07bc780037cf8d9191619c5edf154923b33bf","tid":984630,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:33:11.000Z","msg":"想祝你豬年快樂"},{"pid":"3bb666b0dcbb242487c4277f0cad8c0d25970c41","tid":984630,"uid":26421,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:34:05.000Z","msg":"大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7905c77f25e853db578746fddd7a1ed241897ff","tid":984630,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"人屍飄過來都試過"},{"pid":"51da97eda74b140d7ade3cc49e42746408429bb7","tid":984630,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike"